{
  "video_id": "p_WjntaMORQ",
  "title": "How All You Can Eat Restaurants Make Money",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 280.0,
      "end_time": 2679.0,
      "text": "It's all-you-can-eat pancake time at IHOP."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2680.0,
      "end_time": 4918.0,
      "text": "Endless shrimp is back at Red Lobster."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 4918.0,
      "end_time": 8539.0,
      "text": "all-you-can-eat of this for $6.99?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 8539.0,
      "end_time": 11400.0,
      "text": "[Narrator] Unlimited food."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 11400.0,
      "end_time": 13750.0,
      "text": "These restaurants give you all-you-can-eat"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 13750.0,
      "end_time": 15429.0,
      "text": "for one fixed price."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 15429.0,
      "end_time": 17340.0,
      "text": "Sounds like a pretty good deal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 17340.0,
      "end_time": 20701.0,
      "text": "but how do these restaurants make any money?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 22933.0,
      "end_time": 26380.0,
      "text": "The way buffets typically work is each person pays the same"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 26380.0,
      "end_time": 30600.0,
      "text": "fixed price for access to a line of self-serve dishes."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 30600.0,
      "end_time": 33849.0,
      "text": "You grab a plate, fill it with food, eat, and repeat."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 33849.0,
      "end_time": 36410.0,
      "text": "As many times as you want."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 36411.0,
      "end_time": 39851.0,
      "text": "This started in the 70s and the 80s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 39851.0,
      "end_time": 42123.0,
      "text": "and they were very popular."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 42123.0,
      "end_time": 44184.0,
      "text": "I think it was kind of sign-of-the-time."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 44185.0,
      "end_time": 46504.0,
      "text": "They were a family style restaurant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 46504.0,
      "end_time": 48641.0,
      "text": "they did not serve alcohol,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 48642.0,
      "end_time": 52793.0,
      "text": "but it was a lot of food for not a lot of money."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 52793.0,
      "end_time": 55152.0,
      "text": "[Narrator] Popular chain restaurants that use this model"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 55152.0,
      "end_time": 58414.0,
      "text": "are Golden Corral, and Home Town Buffet."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 58414.0,
      "end_time": 60375.0,
      "text": "Other all-you-can-eat buffets specialize in"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 60375.0,
      "end_time": 63675.0,
      "text": "one type of cuisine, like Chinese food, Indian food,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 63675.0,
      "end_time": 65703.0,
      "text": "or different types of pizza."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 65703.0,
      "end_time": 68374.0,
      "text": "The most obvious money saver for a buffet restaurant"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 68374.0,
      "end_time": 70473.0,
      "text": "is there's less need for servers."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 70473.0,
      "end_time": 73606.0,
      "text": "They don't need full wait staff because you're"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 73606.0,
      "end_time": 77431.0,
      "text": "getting your own food and bringing it to the table."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 77431.0,
      "end_time": 79803.0,
      "text": "[Narrator] But these restaurants apply another strategy"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 79803.0,
      "end_time": 81767.0,
      "text": "that's hidden in plain sight."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 81767.0,
      "end_time": 84642.0,
      "text": "Pay attention to the layout of a buffet line."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 84642.0,
      "end_time": 88210.0,
      "text": "Buffets often put cheaper, or more filling carbs"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 88220.0,
      "end_time": 89458.0,
      "text": "towards the beginning of the line."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 89458.0,
      "end_time": 93136.0,
      "text": "They would have a lot more menu items that had"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 93136.0,
      "end_time": 95542.0,
      "text": "good profit margins on them."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 95543.0,
      "end_time": 99989.0,
      "text": "Then all of the sides and the carbs came before the entree"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 99989.0,
      "end_time": 102328.0,
      "text": "so that by the time you got your entree,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 102328.0,
      "end_time": 103886.0,
      "text": "your plate was full."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 103886.0,
      "end_time": 105698.0,
      "text": "[Narrator] And to try and stop people from taking"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 105698.0,
      "end_time": 108770.0,
      "text": "more than they can eat, these restaurants might provide"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 108770.0,
      "end_time": 110880.0,
      "text": "smaller than average dinner plates."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 110880.0,
      "end_time": 113997.0,
      "text": "Or really big soft-drink cups, so you can fill up on soda."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 113998.0,
      "end_time": 115920.0,
      "text": "But that doesn't always stop people"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 115920.0,
      "end_time": 117710.0,
      "text": "from piling it up vertically."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 117710.0,
      "end_time": 119170.0,
      "text": "Or going back for another plate"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 119170.0,
      "end_time": 120948.0,
      "text": "[Garfield] This will be as an appetizer."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 120948.0,
      "end_time": 123967.0,
      "text": "[Narrator] So some buffets may cut corners in other ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 123968.0,
      "end_time": 126282.0,
      "text": "to make sure they aren't losing a bunch of money."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 126282.0,
      "end_time": 130663.0,
      "text": "Because of the tight profit margins, the food quality"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 130663.00000000001,
      "end_time": 134203.0,
      "text": "wasn't as great as it probably should have been"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 134203.0,
      "end_time": 135592.0,
      "text": "or could have been."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 135592.0,
      "end_time": 138331.0,
      "text": "[Narrator] Riggs says this contributed to their decline."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 138331.0,
      "end_time": 142720.0,
      "text": "Between 1998 and 2017, the number of all-you-can-eat buffets"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 142720.0,
      "end_time": 144392.0,
      "text": "dropped by 26 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 144392.0,
      "end_time": 146649.0,
      "text": "Even though the number of restaurants overall"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 146649.0,
      "end_time": 148232.0,
      "text": "rose by 22 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 149571.0,
      "end_time": 152171.0,
      "text": "Part of the reason for the decline in buffets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 152171.0,
      "end_time": 154315.0,
      "text": "was the expansion of casual dining restaurants"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 154315.0,
      "end_time": 157715.0,
      "text": "like Applebee's, TGI Fridays, Olive Garden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 157715.0,
      "end_time": 160560.0,
      "text": "and Outback Steakhouse."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 160560.0,
      "end_time": 162565.0,
      "text": "This is the type of restaurant that typically offers"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 162565.0,
      "end_time": 164863.0,
      "text": "all-you-can-eat specials on particular items."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 164863.0,
      "end_time": 167936.0,
      "text": "For example, you take Red Lobster,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 167936.0,
      "end_time": 170627.0,
      "text": "they will have their all-you-can-eat shrimp."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 170627.0,
      "end_time": 174270.0,
      "text": "They're not inexpensive and consumers like those"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 174270.0,
      "end_time": 177409.0,
      "text": "and they think they're getting a good value for the money."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 177409.0,
      "end_time": 179197.0,
      "text": "They're around for about six weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 179197.0,
      "end_time": 182128.0,
      "text": "so there's a sense of urgency that's created."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 182128.0,
      "end_time": 184756.0,
      "text": "[Announcer] But hurry, endless shrimp won't be here long."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 184757.0,
      "end_time": 188999.0,
      "text": "The hope is that once consumers get inside the restaurant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 188999.0,
      "end_time": 191440.0,
      "text": "they will add more things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 191440.0,
      "end_time": 196180.0,
      "text": "they'll try, they'll be satisfied, and will return."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 196180.0,
      "end_time": 198760.0,
      "text": "Because the only way you're going to drive your business"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 198760.0,
      "end_time": 200530.0,
      "text": "in the restaurant industry today"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 200530.0,
      "end_time": 203222.0,
      "text": "is through building loyalty."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 203222.0,
      "end_time": 204398.0,
      "text": "[Narrator] With just a few tricks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 204398.0,
      "end_time": 207614.0,
      "text": "like using smaller plates, putting cheap items"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 207614.0,
      "end_time": 211689.0,
      "text": "towards the front, and using drinks to off-set other costs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 211689.0,
      "end_time": 213557.0,
      "text": "all-you-can-eat restaurants are able to accomplish"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 213557.0,
      "end_time": 216117.0,
      "text": "the same goal as any other restaurant."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 216117.0,
      "end_time": 218340.0,
      "text": "Get people in the door."
    }
  ]
}